u1ebfn th\u1ee9c g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m g\u00ec ti\u1ebfp theo th\u00ec b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh dung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o cho hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng?<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p><em><strong>T\u1ea1i tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y \u00edt nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1t kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i thi nh\u01b0 sau<\/strong><\/em><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>H\u1ecdc h\u1ebft t\u1eeb b\u00e0i 25 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0i 50 trong gi\u00e1o tr\u00ecnh Minna no nihongo t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ed1n t\u1eeb v\u1ef1ng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n 600 t\u1eeb, n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc 90 c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p c\u00f9ng h\u01a1n 100 ch\u1eef vi\u1ebft h\u00e1n t\u1ef1.<\/p>\n<p>Th\u00eam n\u1eefa l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00e0i nghe hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecdc hi\u1ec3u th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t v\u00ec<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt li\u1ec7t ph\u1ea7n b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ecdc hi\u1ec3u ho\u1eb7c nghe hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 d\u00f9 l\u00e0 thi JLPT N4 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng n\u1eafm ch\u1eafc k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m b\u00e0i th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c thi tr\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi.<\/p>\n<p>Xem c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ec1 thi \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u00ec sao nh\u00e9:<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-1618 alignnone lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1876px) 100vw, 1876px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291.jpg 1876w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-1024x1024.png 1024w\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt N4 offline\" width=\"1876\" height=\"1876\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291.jpg 1876w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-150x150.png 150w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-300x300.png 300w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-768x768.png 768w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/cautrucdethi-05-1024x1024.png 1024w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1876px) 100vw, 1876px\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea5y, ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ecdc hi\u1ec3u thi c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n b\u00e0i ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m v\u00e0i chi\u1ebfm g\u1ea7n 1 n\u1eeda, cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a 2 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u00e2n b\u1ed1 th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m b\u00e0i th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi gian thi.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n nghe hi\u1ec3u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n thi ri\u00eang chi\u1ebfm \u2153 th\u1eddi gian thi, n\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u00f4n t\u1eadp th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote is-style-default\"><p><strong><em>\u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt N4 ngay t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 th\u00ec c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c chia s\u1ebb sau nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h2><span id=\"II_Nhung_dieu_de_hieu_khi_tu_hoc_tieng_Nhat_N4_tai_nha\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><span id=\"IINhung_dieu_de_hieu_khi_tu_hoc_tieng_Nhat_tai_nha\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><strong>II. Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt N4 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span id=\"1Hoc_1_minh_khong_co_ai_ho_tro\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><strong>H\u1ecdc 1 m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ai h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00f3 bao nhi\u00eau b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 tin n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0? N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u00ec l\u00e0 n\u00f3i \u0111i\u00eau \u0111\u1ea5y.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1edfi ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef kh\u00f3, ngay c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c t\u01b0 duy v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef hay th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng minh c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i khi ch\u1ec9 t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc \u1edf nh\u00e0.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1i kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 m\u00ecnh, ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi, b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc kh\u00f3, hay nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec1u do b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 v\u1ee1 l\u00f2ng m\u00e0 nh\u1eadn ra, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 ai ch\u1ec9 b\u1ea3o cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n l\u00fac m\u1edbi h\u1ecdc s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u d\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 hoang mang v\u00e0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n t\u1eeb b\u1ecf ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn d\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p><strong><em>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u1ecdc N4 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh h\u00e3y xem nh\u1eefng video h\u1ecdc ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadt online mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a Riki nh\u00e9<\/em><\/strong><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<figure>\n<div class=\"rll-youtube-player\" data-id=\"7fbRFZyFS9c\" data-query=\"feature=oembed\">\n<div data-id=\"7fbRFZyFS9c\" data-query=\"feature=oembed\">\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-1.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-1.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<div class=\"play\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><figcaption><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span id=\"2Benh_luoi_hoc\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><strong>\u201cB\u1ec7nh\u201d l\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>T\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 thu n\u1ea1p ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ai hay b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u00e0o. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch g\u00f2 b\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c trung t\u00e2m h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1623 lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-2.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-2.jpg 960w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/anh-bia-facebook-hai-huoc-nhat-mua-thi-300x232.jpg 300w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/anh-bia-facebook-hai-huoc-nhat-mua-thi-768x594.jpg 768w\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt N4 online\" width=\"960\" height=\"743\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-2.jpg 960w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/anh-bia-facebook-hai-huoc-nhat-mua-thi-300x232.jpg 300w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/anh-bia-facebook-hai-huoc-nhat-mua-thi-768x594.jpg 768w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-2.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng\u00a0l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng nguy hi\u1ec3m khi b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 \u201ckh\u00f4ng sao t\u00ed h\u1ecdc c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3\u201d. Th\u1ebf l\u00e0 c\u1ee9 1 ph\u00fat ch\u01a1i, 2 ph\u00fat ch\u01a1i, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t v\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0\u1edbt Facebook, ch\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, xem phim\u2026<\/p>\n<p>Kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn ra m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc th\u00ec th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n, r\u1ed3i b\u1ea1n t\u1eb7c l\u01b0\u1ee1i \u201ck\u1ec7 \u0111i mai h\u1ecdc c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.<\/p>\n<p>Ng\u00e0y n\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y, s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 m\u00e3i d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n l\u1ea1i 1 con s\u1ed1 trong khi k\u1ef3 thi JLPT \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n.<\/p>\n<h3><span id=\"3Hoc_lech_kien_thuc\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><strong>H\u1ecdc l\u1ec7ch ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec nguy hi\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb l\u1ec7ch ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eb7t tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n b\u1ecb l\u1ea7m t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y sang c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1621 lazyloaded\" src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-3.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-3.jpg 900w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/tieng-nhat-N4-online-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/tieng-nhat-N4-online-768x432.jpg 768w\" alt=\"Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt N4 online\" width=\"900\" height=\"506\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-3.jpg 900w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/tieng-nhat-N4-online-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/riki.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/tieng-nhat-N4-online-768x432.jpg 768w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/trungtam.muathemewordpress.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/auto-draft-291-3.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Ti\u1ebfng Nh\u1eadt c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ng\u1eef ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t \u201clo\u1eb1ng ngo\u1eb1ng\u201d n\u00ean n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng v\u00e0 chi ti\u1ebft b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00f2ng lo\u1eb1ng ngo\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t ra ki\u1ec3u g\u00ec.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>NH\u00d3M H\u1eccC TI\u1ebeNG NH\u1eacT MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd TR\u00caN FACEBOOK\u00a0&gt;&gt;\u00a0<em><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/groups\/1246701242142438\/\">THAM GIA NGAY<\/a><\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>TH\u1eec TH\u00c1CH H\u1eccC TI\u1ebeNG NH\u1eacT 20 NG